*Utorak* je drugi dan u nedelji. (Tuesday is the second day of the week.)

Neću biti tu *utorak*. (I won't be here on Tuesday.)

Doći ću u *utorak*. (I will come on Tuesday.)

Sastanak će biti u *utoraku*. (The meeting will be on Tuesday.)

Kupovina se može obaviti u *utorak*. (The purchase can be done on Tuesday.)